name: LFG Korean Ricecakemill (IJM)
description:
This was inspired from a Korean meme coin based on a rice cake called injeolmi. In Korean tradition, we give away rice cake to our neighbors when we move to a new place.

Injeolmi (인절미, pronounced [in.dʑʌl.mi]) is a variety of tteok, or Korean rice cake, made by steaming and pounding glutinous rice flour, which is shaped into small pieces and usually covered with steamed powdered dried beans or other ingredients. - Wikipedia
